<p>67 Any manufacturer or manufacturers of cigarettes who shall
employ opium, marihuana, loco weed, or any other sedative,
narcotic or hypnotic drug, like chemical or substance, either in
the tobacco used or paper wrappers of cigarettes, cigars, tobacco
