App. 2d 685, 167 P.2d 269 (Dist. Ct. App. 1946); Medina v. State,
149 Tex, Crim. 249, 193 S.W.2d 196 (1946) (no error to call
defendant a dealer in marijuana in possession trial). </p>

<p>66 Torres v. State, 161 Tex. Crim. 480, 278 S.W.2d 85 3 (195
